collection

Interface List<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the elements stored in this collection.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>, Iterable<E>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SortedList<E>

    public interface List<E>
extends Collection<E>
    Elements have a position. Adds new behavior needed to process elements with positions. Order does matter, and replacement is allowed. Includes a method to sort elements in this list and iterate with listIterator.
    Author:
    Jacob Malter
